name: Warp Factor 6
overview: You are commander of the Enterprize, touring the galaxy and calling at each space port and time gate. There are three space ports, at the start of the game you are in port one. On leaving this port your position co-ordinates will appear on the display. In order to find the next port press "C". Your aim is now to match your co-ordinates with the co-ordinates of the space port and then land safely in the port. Repeating this operation will give you the co-ordinates of the time gate, your ultimate destination.
